humpty sharma ki dulhania ( english : the bride of humpty sharma , abbreviated as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2014 hindi romantic comedy film written and directed by shashank &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and produced by karan johar . it features varun dhawan as humpty sharma and alia bhatt as kavya pratap singh in the lead roles . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; was released on 11 july 2014 and became a box office success .